WEBVTT

00:00:04.719 --> 00:00:18.699
Bad, you really got a lot better.

00:00:18.699 --> 00:00:21.699
Yeah, he has, thankfully.

00:00:21.699 --> 00:00:24.699
Well, Jehovah has given me 8,000 years to practice.

00:00:24.699 --> 00:00:29.170
Oh, look, they're here!

00:00:29.170 --> 00:00:31.170
Wow!

00:00:31.170 --> 00:00:38.509
What about you, Sophia?

00:00:38.509 --> 00:00:40.509
What do you want to do in paradise?

00:00:40.509 --> 00:00:44.509
Oh, I know. She wants several butterfly garden.

00:00:44.509 --> 00:00:46.509
That would be nice.

00:00:46.509 --> 00:00:58.189
But there's some people I want to meet first.

00:01:08.920 --> 00:01:11.920
Oh, Sophia, that's going to be so beautiful.

00:01:11.920 --> 00:01:13.920
What about you, Caleb?

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:17.920
Well, I kind of just want to be with all of you.

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:23.829
And the monkeys.

00:01:23.829 --> 00:01:26.829
Oh, you love monkeys.

00:01:26.829 --> 00:01:29.829
It's good to imagine ourselves in paradise.

00:01:29.829 --> 00:01:34.829
It helps us to rejoice in the hope that Jehovah has given us.

00:01:34.829 --> 00:01:37.829
Look, Mom, I'm rejoicing in the hope.

00:01:37.829 --> 00:01:39.829
Wee!
